Method Detail

addMode

public void addMode(ModeKey mode,
                    Key accordingKey)
Add a ModeButton to this Button. This saves the ModeButton in a mode-list and registers as an observer to change its mode when ModeButton is pressed.

Parameters:
mode - ModeButton that this Button should be bind to
accordingKey - Key, that should be pressed, when ModeButton is active and Button is pressed

addCurrentMode

public void addCurrentMode(ModeKey mode)
activate a mode. If the button is pressed after this, it will react according to mode preferences. If more than one mode is active afterwards, currently the Button text is set to default!

Parameters:
mode - ModeButton, that should be activated

rmCurrentMode

public void rmCurrentMode(ModeKey mode)
Remove a Mode again, if Mode is not longer active.

Parameters:
mode - ModeButton, that should be deactivated

getPressedKey

public Key getPressedKey()
